  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Referral for cardiac hybrid SPECT/CCTA

          -  Male and female subjects 18 years of age or older

          -  Written informed consent by the participant after information about the project

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Contraindications for coronary CT angiography (including renal failure with a GFR
             &lt;30ml/min/1.73m2, allergies to iodinated contrast agents)

          -  Pregnancy or breast-feeding

          -  Previous coronary revascularisation

          -  Inability to follow the examination procedure (e.g. due to language barriers, severe
             mental disease etc
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
